originalText.text: Dr. Birnbaum is the best. He's attentive and explains everything, and takes pride in his work. He's a great dentist, who also doesn't recommend unnecessary dental work. I've had some bad experiences with other dentists, so it's nice to find someone in my neighborhood who is so good at his job. Highly recommend!

originalText.text: Dr. Birnbaum is an excellent dentist!  I have been seeing him for at least 12 years. He has always shown great skill, thoroughness, and honesty! He has an excellent bedside manner and genuinely cares about his patients and takes a great deal of pride in his work.

originalText.text: I've only recently switched over to Dr. Birnbaum although I've known him for a while.  I can't say enough how pleased I am and how impressed I am with his work and the facilities at his practice.  He is engaging and explains what he is doing or needs to be doing for you using real-time, close-up images (not x-rays) of the teeth that needs attention and, after he is done, the post-procedure image so you can tell the difference.  I am so glad I switched.

originalText.text: I am taking the time to write my Review because Dr. Birnbaum has become one of my favorite Dentist. I highly recommend Dr.Birnbaum for your Dental needs now and in the future. He is in it for all the right reasons, and makes decisions primarily based on treatment needs. I really love my interaction with the Office staff as well. Dr. Birnbaum is Professional, Friendly and takes a personal interest in his Patients. I became a new Patient recently May 2019 and was very pleased with my dental experience.

originalText.text: My husband and I are new patients.  We both had cleaning.  I was impressed with how thorough and transparent the doctor is.  He wouldn't recommend something that isn't necessary.  He made sure our insurance covered all I needed.  And most importantly he made me feel at ease.  I had bad dental experiences before and I'm always terrified.  He did every filling painlessly.  My teeth look great now!  And I don't have as much sensitivity as I used to.  Thank you so much!
